abstract: >-
  Open-source desktop AI design tool. Generate HTML prototypes, slide decks,
  and marketing assets from natural-language prompts. Multi-model BYOK
  (Anthropic, OpenAI, Gemini, DeepSeek, Ollama). Local-first. The open
  counterpart to Claude Design.
